{
  "chapter": 20,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十回 不祥预兆。竹叶青与紫铃密谋利用黑杀组织对付阿吉，紫铃实为大老板安插的奸细却早已倒向竹叶青。云中金刚崔老三受竹叶青雇佣带来九名黑杀成员，但他深知这些人是去送死。崔老三索取字据和十万两银子作为报酬，还想要紫铃，竹叶青假意答应后趁其不备以暗藏之剑将其刺杀。紫铃惊觉竹叶青竟是深藏不露的剑术高手，更加死心塌地。竹叶青命紫铃去招待黑杀众人，驼背老人前来传信。与此同时，阿吉夜访大牛家，发现大牛一家失踪，只有苗子对着一桌丰盛酒菜发怔，预示着不祥之兆。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "因为像你这样的女人，我是死也舍不得送给别人的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 3,
      "line_end": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "不管怎么样，灌米汤的本事，你总可以算天下第一。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 5,
      "line_end": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "别的本事难道我就比别人差了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "你若不比别人强，我怎么会死心塌地的跟着你？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "我笑那个老乌龟，居然叫我到你这里来做奸细，他若知道我们的事，不气得跳楼才怪！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "那也只因为你实在太会做戏，居然能让他以为你最讨厌我，居然能让他做了活王八还在自鸣得意。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "可是我也弄不懂你究竟在搞什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "我搞了什么鬼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "你是不是又替那老乌龟约了一批帮手来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "嗯！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "你约的是些什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "你有没有听说'黑杀'这两个字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 27,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "黑杀是一个人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 29,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "不是一个人，是一群人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "他们为什么要替自己取这么不吉祥的名字？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "因为他们本来就像是瘟疫一样，无论谁遇着他们，都很难保住性命！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "他们是些什么样的人！",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "各式各样的人都有，有的出身下五门，也有些是从武当、少林这些名门正派中被逐出的弟子，甚至有些是从东海扶桑岛上，流落到中土来的浪人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "难道他们每个人都有一身好功夫？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "可是他们真正可怕的地方，不是他们的武功！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "是他们既不要脸，也不要命！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "这种人的确很难对付！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "所以你才奇怪，我为什么要他们来帮那老乌龟对付阿吉？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "嗯！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "你为什么不想想，现在连铁虎都已死了，若没有这些人来保护他，他怎么敢去见阿吉？阿吉若连他的面都见不到，怎么能要他死？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "有了这些人来保护他，他还会死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "只有死得更快些！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "难道连这些人都不是阿吉的对手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "绝不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "所以这次他已死定了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "大概是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "可是你还忘了一点。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "哦！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "大老板死了后，阿吉要对付的人就是你了！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "很可能！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "到了那时候，你准备怎么办？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "难道你已经有了对付他的法子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 85,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "你有把握？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "我几时做过没有把握的事？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "等到这件事一过去，你当然就是大老板了，我呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "你当然就是老板娘！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "你最好记住，老板娘只有一个，否则……",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "speaker_name": "崔老三",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "是我崔老三。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "text": "请进来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "speaker_name": "崔老三",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "这个女人是谁？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "text": "她是我们自己人，没关系！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "这个崔老三，就是那个'云中金刚'崔老三？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "我们多年前在辽北道上就已认得。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "所以你早就知道铁虎不是他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "text": "现在不管铁虎是谁，都没关系了，我已经替你杀了他。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "speaker_name": "崔老三",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "他的尸体还在不在？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "text": "就在外面，你随时都可以带走！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "text": "我要的人呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "speaker_name": "崔老三",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "我说过负责带他们来，他们就一定会来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "text": "九个人都来！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "speaker_name": "崔老三",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "一个都不会少！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "text": "在哪里见面？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "speaker_name": "崔老三",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "他们也喜欢女人，他们都听说过这里有个韩大奶奶。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "text": "现在韩大奶奶虽已不在了，我还是保证可以让他们满意。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "speaker_name": "崔老三",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "你应该让他们满意，因为这已是他们最后一次。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "text": "怎么会是最后一次！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "speaker_name": "崔老三",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "你自己应该知道，他们这次来，并不是来杀人，而来送死的！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "text": "送死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "speaker_name": "崔老三",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "那个阿吉既然能杀铁虎，就一定也可以杀他们！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "text": "看来我好像什么事都瞒不过你。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "speaker_name": "崔老三",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "我能够活到现在，并不是全靠运气。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "text": "所以你一定还能活下去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "speaker_name": "崔老三",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "哼！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "text": "而且我保证你一定会活得比以前逍遥自在。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "speaker_name": "崔老三",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "text": "所以别人就算真不幸死了，你也不必要伤心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "speaker_name": "崔老三",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "我虽然也入了黑教，但那些人却不是我的朋友！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "text": "他们还不配做你的朋友。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "speaker_name": "崔老三",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "我根本就没有朋友，连一个朋友都没有，因为我从不相信任何人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "text": "所以我说的话，你也不太相信？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "text": "但是我可以给你保证！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "speaker_name": "崔老三",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "什么保证？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "text": "你要什么都行！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "speaker_name": "崔老三",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "我要你亲笔写一张字据，说明你要我做了些什么。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "text": "行！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "speaker_name": "崔老三",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "我要你在明天中午之前，把十万两现银存入'利源'银号我的账户里去！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "text": "行！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "speaker_name": "崔老三",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "我还要这个女人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "text": "这一点更容易，你现在就可以把她带走！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_cui_lao_san",
      "text": "你一定想不到我还会用剑？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "非但他想不到，连我都想不到！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "想不到我会用剑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "你非但会用剑，而且还一定是个高手！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "现在你总该已明白了，我不但是高手，而且还是高手中的高手！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "可是你一定知道我绝不会泄漏你的秘密，就好像我早就知道你绝不会把我送给别人一样。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "只要你信任我，什么事我都替你做！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "现在我就有样事要你做！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "去替韩大奶奶招呼黑杀的兄弟，想法子要他们一切满意，他们才会为大老板拼命，拼命去杀阿吉，阿吉就绝不会放过他们了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "text": "你是什么人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "驼背老人",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "我是来报讯的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "text": "是什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "驼背老人",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "黑杀的兄弟已提早到了，正在韩大奶奶那里等着姑娘去！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "紫铃",
      "listener": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "text": "你是不是要陪我去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "驼背老人",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "叶先生再三吩咐．只要我离开姑娘一步，我这两条腿就要被砍掉喂狗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_zi",
      "speaker_name": "苗子",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "坐。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    }
